bear-service
===


Explanation
------------------------
Example of service:

template structure of microservice build on docker.

1) In build.sbt you need to change config for docker base image and docker repository to publish to.

2) /src/main/scala/io.mikroservice/api contain declarations of service endpoints

3) /src/main/scala/io.mikroservice/domain contain core logic of service

4) /src/main/scala/io.mikroservice/infrastructure contain core logic of dependent services
